471
00:33:58,080 --> 00:33:59,040
O, ako ga želite okrenuti, točno.

472
00:33:59,440 --> 00:33:59,520
Da.

473
00:33:59,680 --> 00:33:59,760
Da.

474
00:34:00,160 --> 00:34:00,640
To je vjerojatno to.

475
